::DarkMouse::

She felt uneasy about this whole thing.  They would be out gunned, 
out numbered, out everything.  And all she had was a rifle, a few 
daggers, and her little energon pistol.  She was also programmed to 
be a scout, and computer wiz.  Not fighting.  She turned and looked 
back at the base.  She hoped she would see her pet rat again and 
soon.  She wondered what plan Megatron had thought of and what his 
plan was.  She followed orders and followed Megatron into battle.
But she had a bad feeling about this whole thing.
